<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīramaṇīyuṁḍu sujanādhāruṁḍu vibudha
<lb n="2" break="no"/>nutaguṇanidhānuṁḍu vijaya <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīramyamūrtti
<lb n="3"/>gētama gārāpuṁ danūjuṁ ḍabhayakaruṁḍu vogaḍa <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="4"/>velanāṁṭikiṁ doḍavanaṁgā velasina kuṟuṁgaḍalu
<lb n="5"/>galugu vīruṁḍu nijadō <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> rbbalamunu balimiyuṁ bā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ḍiyuṁ galavāṁ ḍadhikārapadavi galavāṁḍu mahini [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>2*]
<lb n="7"/>śakamahipālakasaṁvatsaramulu śaśinidhiviyadi
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṁddusaṁkhyagāṁ gīrttisukaruṁḍu rājēṁdracōḍani yiṣṭa
<lb n="9" break="no"/>subhaṭuṁḍḍu veṁggaḍayasutuṁḍu sūryyāṁkkuṁ ḍakala
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṁkkuṁḍaina kṣīrārāmadēvuṁḍagu śaṁbhunaku bhaktuṁḍai śa
<lb n="11" break="no"/>nibhavani prakaṭiṁppa niṣkasaptaka micce moṭṭapaṟiti kāṁpu
<lb n="12" break="no"/>lakunuṁ baragu sānulaku <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">3</supplied>
<lb n="13"/>śrīmatukṣīrārāmīśvaramuna sānimunnūrvvu vāḍaru
<lb n="14" break="no"/>nāyakulu mallamārēniki naṭṭavavrittiyu nāvajava
<lb n="15" break="no"/>vrittiyu nācaṁdrārkkamugā niccitimi <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> dīninevva
</p>

<p>1) Some space below this line is left blank.</p>

<p>
<lb n="16" break="no"/>rēni vilaṁbbhamu sēsinavāru gōbrāhmaṇavadha sēsi
<lb n="17" break="no"/>navāru <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> peddakoḍuku kapālamunaṁ guḍicinavāru <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

